<p><em>Editor&rsquo;s Note:</em> On the last Monday of each month, Lori Gottlieb <a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/category/dear-therapist/">answers a reader’s question</a> about a problem, big or small. Have a question? Email her at <a href="mailto:dear.therapist@theatlantic.com">dear.therapist@theatlantic.com</a>.<br />
